Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Margaret Thatcher's re-election and the 'special relationship', 1983
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00ydmnl
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 10 Jun 1983
Margaret Thatcher's dedication to the 'special relationship' between Britain and America, and journalist James "Scotty" Reston's correct prediction on Thatcher's re-election.